1
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,719
Why are you standing here?

2
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:58,760
Are you cold?

3
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,079
Mr. Chen.

4
00:02:04,079 --> 00:02:05,439
I want to

5
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,760
clear my head.

6
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,080
Why?

7
00:02:12,319 --> 00:02:14,120
I have to make myself remember that

8
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,039
the person standing before me

9
00:02:16,319 --> 00:02:17,439
is no ordinary man,

10
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,439
but a Grand Secretary of the court.

11
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,639
I see.

12
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:25,159
You're taking a jab at me.

13
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,039
Telling me to realize that

14
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:28,319
from now on,

15
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:30,960
not to put on airs with you.

16
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,680
I wouldn't dare.

17
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:35,960
I promise that from now on,

18
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,479
I'll arrive before you do,

19
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,439
so you won't have to wait for me.

20
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,199
I never said that.

21
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,080
I understand.

22
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,759
[Looking at him today,]

23
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,560
[something seems to be different.]

24
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,280
People connected to Prince Glorian

25
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:58,280
are more than we originally thought,

26
00:02:59,039 --> 00:03:01,240
and many serve in the Ministry of Revenue.

27
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,240
They've all been replaced this time,

28
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:06,120
leaving the Ministry

29
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,479
critically short-staffed.

30
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:11,159
Though your father lacked personal virtue,

31
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,000
he

32
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:14,599
had nothing to do with Prince Glorian,

33
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,879
and no remarkable relationship with others.

34
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,840
So,

35
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,759
after much deliberation,

36
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,520
I've decided

37
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,199
to keep him on.

38
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,199
What do you think?

39
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,639
These are court affairs.

40
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:33,080
You don't need to ask me.

41
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:34,719
But,

42
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,240
he is, after all, your father.

43
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:43,280
Oh right,

44
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,520
There's something I want to ask you.

45
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:48,159
Why did you

46
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,719
help Ye Xian so much?

47
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,800
You mean,

48
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,400
delivering the letter for him?

49
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,120
Could it be that

50
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:59,360
you deliberately let the information reach me

51
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,319
so I would go warn him?

52
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,879
Although I deliberately

53
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,719
had you deliver the letter for him,

54
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:08,280
you still had to agree to it yourself.

55
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,000
You knew full well

56
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,199
how dangerous this was.

57
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,759
You were tied up,

58
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:13,919
and you nearly lost your life.

59
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,919
Yet you risked everything to help him.

60
00:04:17,039 --> 00:04:17,639
Why?

61
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:19,720
Because

62
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:24,040
he has also risked himself many times for me.

63
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:25,120
To me,

64
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,600
he is a true friend.

65
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,079
Just a friend?

66
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:55,519
What about me?

67
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:00,839
If I also encountered

68
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:02,079
something this dangerous,

69
00:05:03,319 --> 00:05:04,399
would you also help me?

70
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,160
I would.

71
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,680
So I am also your friend.

72
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,199
Yes.

73
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,759
Ever since I entered the Grand Secretariat,

74
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,759
matchmakers have been constantly visiting.

75
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,680
My grandmother and teacher

76
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:23,720
have also been pressing me.

77
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,560
You are so young,

78
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,120
and already a Grand Secretary.

79
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,560
In this capital,

80
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,040
anyone with a daughter to marry off

81
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:34,319
would naturally want to be related to you.

82
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:35,720
Really?

83
00:05:41,319 --> 00:05:42,000
What about you?

84
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:45,879
Me?

85
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,720
I don't want

86
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:04,839
to be just your friend.

87
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,680
Don't move. Listen to me.

88
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,160
We've been through so much together.

89
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:11,959
Are you willing

90
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:13,600
to marry me?

91
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,079
What kind of joke is this?

92
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:00,399
It never crossed my mind

93
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:01,959
that you would say this to me.

94
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,439
If I had known

95
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,439
you were going to say this,

96
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,000
I wouldn't have come today.

97
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:07,639
It never crossed my mind

98
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:08,600
that we would be together.

99
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,079
If you've never thought about it,

100
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,399
start thinking about it from today.

101
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:20,279
No need.

102
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,240
I've already made up my mind.

103
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:24,560
I'm never getting married in this lifetime.

104
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:26,560
I'll go to Shanxi to run a business.

105
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,519
At that time, you should find

106
00:07:28,519 --> 00:07:29,040
a woman

107
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,240
who is a suitable match for you.

108
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:31,680
I have things to do.

109
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:33,839
I need to go back first.

110
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:01,839
So,

111
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,839
Mr. Chen proposed to you?

112
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:07,800
And you turned him down?

113
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,040
Are you crazy, miss?

114
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,279
That's Mr. Chen!

115
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:13,560
Lord Grand Secretary!

116
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:15,839
So what?

117
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,040
The more powerful a man is,

118
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,519
the more wives and concubines he has.

119
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:22,120
The Chen family is a complicated household.

120
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,439
If I marry him,

121
00:08:23,759 --> 00:08:24,519
I wouldn't be able to control the family,

122
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:25,480
nor stop them.

123
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,519
Besides,

124
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,639
after what happened with my mother,

125
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,319
I no longer

126
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,720
have any hope for marriage.

127
00:08:32,439 --> 00:08:34,000
Even if it's Mr. Chen,

128
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:35,279
no exception.

129
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:38,840
I,

130
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,279
I thought you liked him.

131
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:44,720
I do like him, but it doesn't mean

132
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,799
I have to marry him.

133
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:48,879
Think about it,

134
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:51,679
now grandmother loves me,

135
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,679
father can't control me.

136
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,360
I have some money of my own.

137
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:56,720
I should just

138
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,759
live freely and happily.

139
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,519
Why must I marry

140
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,759
and get trapped in the family,

141
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:03,399
asking for trouble?

142
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,080
But...

143
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,879
-But...
-No more buts.

144
00:09:09,279 --> 00:09:10,440
No matter how much I like him,

145
00:09:10,519 --> 00:09:11,919
I like myself more.

146
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,399
Besides,

147
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:17,279
I still have

148
00:09:17,279 --> 00:09:18,519
many business matters.

149
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:21,000
That batch of tea I shipped from Jiangnan

150
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,000
should be arriving soon.

151
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:23,799
That's the first shipment

152
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:24,879
going to Shanxi.

153
00:09:25,759 --> 00:09:26,879
I was actually thinking

154
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,039
I should go to Shanxi

155
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:29,320
with that shipment.

156
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,440
Just hear the shopkeepers' reports

157
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:35,159
without seeing it in person,

158
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:37,080
I still feel uneasy.

159
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,200
Miss...

160
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:58,519
What's this?

161
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:01,519
When you just came of the age of 15,

162
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:02,919
the mistress started

163
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:04,200
embroidering this wedding gown.

164
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:06,200
She was afraid you'd see it

165
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:07,639
and be upset,

166
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,320
so she always did it secretly.

167
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,159
That morning,

168
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,080
I saw the Madam...

169
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:17,799
This wedding gown and the letter

170
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,039
were placed right next to her.

171
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:20,919
The letter she left

172
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,600
told me to put the gown away for now.

173
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,440
Waiting for your wedding day

174
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:26,720
to give it to you.

175
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:30,759
But I just heard

176
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,200
what you said to Qingpu,

177
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:34,399
I took the liberty of thinking

178
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:35,639
that

179
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,919
I should give it to you now.

180
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:04,039
My daughter Jinzhao,

181
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,159
after my death,

182
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:08,799
the one I worry about most is you.

183
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,159
I am a useless person.

184
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:17,919
I have done many wrong things in my life.

185
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,639
The two biggest mistakes,

186
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,000
one,

187
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,840
marrying your father;

188
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,279
the other,

189
00:11:26,879 --> 00:11:28,720
sending you away to Tongzhou,

190
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,799
letting two of us be separated.

191
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:33,639
This wedding gown,

192
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:36,039
I sewed for you in person.

193
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,519
The craftsmanship is passable,

194
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:39,240
but at least it's finished.

195
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,919
But right now,

196
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:44,240
I don't know if leaving it to you

197
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,519
is right or wrong.

198
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:52,039
You see, I am truly a muddled person,

199
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,600
muddled my whole life.

200
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,159
By now,

201
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:57,559
I don't even have the strength to regret.

202
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,639
Whether you marry or not,

203
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,080
this wedding gown,

204
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:04,080
just keep it as a memento.

205
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,799
Good girl,

206
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,159
you are smarter than I am.

207
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:09,960
I have only one hope for you.

208
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,080
In all things,

209
00:12:11,279 --> 00:12:12,720
learn from your grandmother.

210
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:15,440
Stand on your own feet wherever you go.

211
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,559
Whatever you do,

212
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:20,320
do not end up like me.

213
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:56,279
Daughter-in-law.

214
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:59,279
We fill the gap every year,

215
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:02,080
why does it keep getting bigger?

216
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,200
Mother,

217
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:07,559
the household surplus has never been large.

218
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,279
And this year's social visits and gift exchanges

219
00:13:10,519 --> 00:13:11,639
have increased somewhat.

220
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:16,279
It's all my fault for managing this.

221
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,679
It's not your fault.

222
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,200
For this whole household,

223
00:13:22,639 --> 00:13:23,440
it's normal that

224
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,960
income falls short of expenditure.

225
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,639
The dowry list for Gu Lian,

226
00:13:29,639 --> 00:13:30,519
is it ready?

227
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:34,000
I was just about to mention that.

228
00:13:35,679 --> 00:13:38,240
Extravagant weddings are all the rage now.

229
00:13:38,919 --> 00:13:40,600
The Yao family has four sons.

230
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:42,480
Yao Wenxiu is the fourth.

231
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:45,080
Gu Lian will have three sisters-in-law.

232
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,759
Among them,

233
00:13:47,919 --> 00:13:49,519
comparisons are inevitable.

234
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,919
If Gu Lian has less dowry,

235
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:53,720
she might be mistreated.

236
00:13:55,519 --> 00:13:56,960
You don't need to hint around.

237
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,279
I may shortchange others,

238
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,120
but I won't

239
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:01,399
shortchange Gu Lian.

240
00:14:06,759 --> 00:14:07,879
It's just that this shortfall,

241
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:09,279
it's far too large.

242
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,879
I keep hearing

243
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,879
that Dezhao's properties

244
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,159
in recent years

245
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,679
have been doing quite well.

246
00:14:26,519 --> 00:14:27,559
Dezhao's properties

247
00:14:27,559 --> 00:14:28,559
have always been helped with management

248
00:14:28,559 --> 00:14:29,639
by the Ji family.

249
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,879
They are professional,

250
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:34,080
of course manage it well.

251
00:14:37,519 --> 00:14:38,240
Mother,

252
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,200
what are you suggesting?

253
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,120
Here's what I think.

254
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,919
Dezhao's wife is gone.

255
00:14:50,519 --> 00:14:51,720
A widower like him,

256
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,879
raising a child on his own,

257
00:14:53,159 --> 00:14:54,120
it's not proper.

258
00:14:55,799 --> 00:14:56,879
As his mother,

259
00:14:57,159 --> 00:14:58,200
I can't just stand by

260
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,320
and do nothing.

261
00:14:59,639 --> 00:15:00,600
If people heard of this,

262
00:15:00,759 --> 00:15:02,080
I'll be the one blamed.

263
00:15:04,279 --> 00:15:05,080
So how about

264
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:07,480
letting Dezhao and his family

265
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:08,799
move back here?

266
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:15,279
What do you think?

267
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,679
Have you found out

268
00:15:16,679 --> 00:15:17,840
where Jinzhao is going this time?

269
00:15:18,759 --> 00:15:19,480
When does she plan

270
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,720
to return to the capital?

271
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:23,519
She's been here for nearly three years.

272
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:24,320
That's unreasonable.

273
00:15:24,759 --> 00:15:26,080
She's not planning to return to the capital.

274
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,399
It sounds like she's doing business.

275
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,919
She brought in a shipload of goods

276
00:15:29,919 --> 00:15:31,000
from Jiangnan.

277
00:15:31,519 --> 00:15:32,759
She went to the warehouse early this morning

278
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,320
and only just came back.

279
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:37,000
And that the old lady too.

280
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,360
She didn't even bother to inform

281
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,360
me, the head wife,

282
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,039
not even once.

283
00:15:40,399 --> 00:15:41,559
Just letting her stay observing mourning.

284
00:15:41,759 --> 00:15:42,279
Does she really think this is

285
00:15:42,279 --> 00:15:43,360
Gu Jinzhao's own home?

286
00:15:43,919 --> 00:15:44,679
And Ji Yao?

287
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:45,759
Mr. Ji too,

288
00:15:45,759 --> 00:15:47,200
just back from checking the shops in Xianghe.

289
00:15:47,519 --> 00:15:48,840
He heard Miss Gu had come,

290
00:15:49,039 --> 00:15:49,679
rushed straight over

291
00:15:49,679 --> 00:15:50,519
to her courtyard.

292
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:52,519
My foolish son.

293
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:54,080
Go and run an errand.

294
00:15:54,519 --> 00:15:55,360
Just say,

295
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:56,879
say that I'm not feeling well,

296
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,159
and tell him to come back.

297
00:15:58,559 --> 00:15:59,120
Yes.

298
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,679
Never mind.

299
00:16:00,879 --> 00:16:01,639
I'll go myself.

300
00:16:10,519 --> 00:16:12,279
[Then start thinking about it from today.]

301
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,080
[I'll wait for your answer.]

302
00:16:36,279 --> 00:16:37,000
So,

303
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,399
you already know everything?

304
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:40,840
Explain yourself.

305
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,679
Secretly

306
00:16:42,679 --> 00:16:44,320
buying land

307
00:16:44,679 --> 00:16:45,799
and setting up shops in Shanxi,

308
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:46,799
what are you doing?

309
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,360
Since when was I being secretive?

310
00:16:49,559 --> 00:16:51,159
If I really wanted to hide it,

311
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,600
do you think you could have found out?

312
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,519
So you think you're in the right, do you?

313
00:16:54,679 --> 00:16:55,240
Gu Jinzhao,

314
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,200
what exactly are you trying to do?

315
00:16:57,399 --> 00:16:58,759
I'm not trying to do anything.

316
00:17:00,519 --> 00:17:02,120
I just heard that in Shanxi,

317
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:04,000
women are relatively free to run business.

318
00:17:04,399 --> 00:17:06,160
Maybe I'll go there someday,

319
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:08,680
so I'm making preparations in advance.

320
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:12,720
Women were relatively free,

321
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,039
what does that mean?

322
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,440
And when is 'someday'?

323
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,960
You're not planning to get married?

324
00:17:20,279 --> 00:17:21,599
I never planned to get married.

325
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:22,279
Absurd.

326
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,839
What are you doing?

327
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:26,880
-You scared me.
-You scared me.

328
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,759
I don't agree.

329
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:33,720
Not to mention grandmother,

330
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:34,880
I'm the first to disagree.

331
00:17:35,119 --> 00:17:36,200
What right do you have to disagree?

332
00:17:36,319 --> 00:17:37,039
I have the right—

333
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:43,920
I know.

334
00:17:44,599 --> 00:17:45,880
Because of what happened with your mother,

335
00:17:46,839 --> 00:17:48,240
you're frightened, scared.

336
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:49,839
But...

337
00:17:50,079 --> 00:17:51,519
But this is like doing business.

338
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,400
Lots of people lose their entire investment.

339
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,559
It doesn't mean everyone should just give up.

340
00:17:59,279 --> 00:17:59,880
You don't understand.

341
00:18:00,279 --> 00:18:01,319
What don't I understand?

342
00:18:09,079 --> 00:18:10,359
If you're scared,

343
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,440
why not just marry me?

344
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:14,039
What nonsense are you talking?

345
00:18:14,359 --> 00:18:15,599
I'm not talking nonsense.

346
00:18:16,119 --> 00:18:17,000
Grandmother,

347
00:18:17,119 --> 00:18:17,799
didn't she also hope that

348
00:18:17,799 --> 00:18:18,920
we would be together?

349
00:18:20,079 --> 00:18:21,119
Do you like me?

350
00:18:22,279 --> 00:18:22,880
I...

351
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:27,680
I... the reason is because

352
00:18:28,279 --> 00:18:30,039
I worry about you.

353
00:18:30,519 --> 00:18:31,920
I'm afraid you'll never marry.

354
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:33,640
Once you marry me,

355
00:18:34,039 --> 00:18:35,039
I guarantee that for the rest of your life

356
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,720
you'll never have to be afraid again.

357
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:39,799
Greetings, Mrs. Song.

358
00:18:40,319 --> 00:18:40,839
Quick, quick, quick—

359
00:18:40,839 --> 00:18:41,400
Mrs. Song.

360
00:18:45,359 --> 00:18:45,759
Mother.

361
00:18:45,759 --> 00:18:46,720
Greetings, auntie.

362
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,279
So late at night,

363
00:18:49,519 --> 00:18:50,680
why do you have the door shut?

364
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,200
We were discussing

365
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:55,200
investing in draft banks in Jiangnan.

366
00:18:56,319 --> 00:18:57,000
It's confidential,

367
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:58,079
so we had to shut the door.

368
00:18:59,519 --> 00:19:00,799
I see.

369
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:03,039
Your father

370
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:04,400
wants you to come see him.

371
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:06,279
He has something to tell you.

372
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:09,160
Yes.

373
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,440
Jinzhao,

374
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,759
the mourning period is almost over.

375
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,640
When do you plan to return to the capital?

376
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,680
I haven't thought about it.

377
00:19:25,039 --> 00:19:25,680
What?

378
00:19:26,799 --> 00:19:27,559
Auntie,

379
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:29,160
do you not want me to stay?

380
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,079
How would I dare?

381
00:19:33,359 --> 00:19:35,440
Though you are not a member of our family,

382
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,960
you are the old lady's favorite child.

383
00:19:38,759 --> 00:19:40,920
How could I dare refuse to let you stay?

384
00:19:47,519 --> 00:19:48,160
Miss,

385
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,759
why is she speaking

386
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:51,039
with such a sharp tongue?

387
00:19:51,839 --> 00:19:52,400
Never mind.

388
00:19:53,279 --> 00:19:54,359
For Second Brother's sake,

389
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:55,519
I won't argue with her.

390
00:19:56,799 --> 00:19:58,160
I just sent word to the palace

391
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,200
that I wasn't feeling well,

392
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:00,400
and took a half day off.

393
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:01,559
Mr. Chen,

394
00:20:01,799 --> 00:20:02,640
didn't you say you wanted Miss Gu

395
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:03,279
to observe the mourning period in peace

396
00:20:03,279 --> 00:20:04,440
and give her plenty of time to consider?

397
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,240
So why now

398
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:06,240
are you chasing after her?

399
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:08,079
A few days ago,

400
00:20:08,079 --> 00:20:09,599
she brought in goods from Jiangnan,

401
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:11,559
planning to send them to Shanxi for sale.

402
00:20:12,839 --> 00:20:13,440
She is

403
00:20:13,599 --> 00:20:14,960
extremely cautious when it comes to business.

404
00:20:16,119 --> 00:20:16,960
I'm afraid that

405
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,359
since she likes to handle things personally,

406
00:20:19,559 --> 00:20:21,720
she might follow these goods to Shanxi.

407
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,000
Then the delay could lead to trouble.
(Watch on www,kisskh,la to support Admin)

408
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:26,200
Let's go.

409
00:20:31,079 --> 00:20:32,279
Alright. Go back.

410
00:20:44,079 --> 00:20:44,720
Miss Gu.

411
00:20:46,839 --> 00:20:47,440
Mr. Ping.

412
00:20:47,559 --> 00:20:48,720
The horses were already fed.

413
00:20:48,839 --> 00:20:50,680
We can leave after a quarter-hour.

414
00:20:51,279 --> 00:20:51,759
Good.

415
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:53,359
Mr. Ping,

416
00:20:53,519 --> 00:20:54,920
a mighty dragon can't crush a local snake.

417
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:55,920
Once you arrive,

418
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,960
pay respects to the local powers.

419
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,519
Don't rush to compete either.

420
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:00,920
Sell at whatever price

421
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:01,960
the others are selling at.

422
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:04,720
It's even fine

423
00:21:04,799 --> 00:21:05,720
to charge half a percent more than them.

424
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:06,799
Better not to make enemies.

425
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:11,279
After you've established a foothold,

426
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,160
business will follow.

427
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:14,759
Then I'll

428
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:16,039
go check on the other matters.

429
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:21,839
Inspect everything carefully.

430
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:24,920
Let's go, miss.

431
00:21:28,759 --> 00:21:29,319
Miss.

432
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:30,720
Mr. Chen.

433
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:43,799
Why is he here?

434
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:52,440
Mr. Chen.

435
00:21:53,279 --> 00:21:54,000
Gu Jinzhao,

436
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,160
is this the final answer

437
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:56,920
you're giving me?

438
00:21:59,160 --> 00:22:00,240
Do you really not want

439
00:22:01,079 --> 00:22:02,359
to think it over properly?

440
00:22:04,880 --> 00:22:05,359
I...

441
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:06,759
I really...

442
00:22:07,279 --> 00:22:08,759
I really shouldn't have indulged you.

443
00:22:09,039 --> 00:22:10,279
You just leave without a word,

444
00:22:10,279 --> 00:22:11,640
off to Shanxi all of a sudden?

445
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:15,279
Who said I'm going to Shanxi?

446
00:22:15,599 --> 00:22:16,559
I just wanted to

447
00:22:16,559 --> 00:22:17,680
see Mr. Ping off.

448
00:22:20,599 --> 00:22:21,720
Let me, let me, let me...

449
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,400
So you're not going to Shanxi?

450
00:22:28,759 --> 00:22:29,279
Careful!

451
00:22:33,039 --> 00:22:33,960
In that case,

452
00:22:34,279 --> 00:22:35,240
you go ahead with your business.

453
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:36,880
I...

454
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:40,119
I'll go have some tea,

455
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:41,559
and wait for you.

456
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:47,400
Miss,

457
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:48,720
we can leave now.

458
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:50,920
Be careful.

459
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:53,079
Take care, Miss.

460
00:22:56,759 --> 00:22:57,519
Let's go.

461
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,480
[This man,]

462
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:24,319
[seems to have changed.]

463
00:23:35,119 --> 00:23:36,279
You're off duty today?

464
00:23:37,519 --> 00:23:38,119
No.

465
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:45,960
Then that means

466
00:23:46,519 --> 00:23:47,640
the court isn't busy?

467
00:23:48,559 --> 00:23:49,480
Nothing much going on?

468
00:23:58,039 --> 00:24:00,200
My grandmother has gone to Baoping.

469
00:24:00,559 --> 00:24:02,839
Second Brother returned to the capital today.

470
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:06,680
Uncle and aunt are both here.

471
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:08,319
How about I invite them out

472
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:10,000
to keep you company, Mr. Chen?

473
00:24:10,880 --> 00:24:12,640
I haven't even finished a cup of tea,

474
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:14,039
and you're already trying to chase me away?

475
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:16,240
No, not at all.

476
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:19,400
That's good.

477
00:24:19,759 --> 00:24:20,720
No need to see anyone else.

478
00:24:21,799 --> 00:24:22,519
Today,

479
00:24:22,839 --> 00:24:23,680
I came to see you.

480
00:24:38,799 --> 00:24:39,359
You

481
00:24:40,359 --> 00:24:41,279
You... you stay still.

482
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,559
Let's talk this out calmly.

483
00:24:46,799 --> 00:24:47,440
Alright.

484
00:24:49,799 --> 00:24:51,640
What I said to you at Baoxiang Temple,

485
00:24:52,599 --> 00:24:53,359
did you ever

486
00:24:53,359 --> 00:24:54,240
actually give it any serious thought?

487
00:24:55,799 --> 00:24:56,640
Which part?

488
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,519
About taking me into consideration.

489
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:03,319
Didn't I already tell you?

490
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:04,759
I'm not considering it.

491
00:25:07,039 --> 00:25:08,279
Gu Jinzhao.

492
00:25:10,519 --> 00:25:11,640
With you acting like this,

493
00:25:11,799 --> 00:25:13,319
you expect me to speak calmly with you?

494
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:14,359
Come back to the capital with me.

495
00:25:17,359 --> 00:25:19,000
Maybe with you right under my nose,

496
00:25:19,519 --> 00:25:20,880
you'll actually be able to think clearly.

497
00:25:21,559 --> 00:25:21,960
You...

498
00:25:23,599 --> 00:25:24,000
Hey!

499
00:25:24,759 --> 00:25:26,400
You're abusing your power!

500
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:28,079
Once in a while, what's the harm?

501
00:25:29,279 --> 00:25:30,519
Anyway, your family

502
00:25:30,519 --> 00:25:31,759
hasn't submitted accounts to me in a while.

503
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,079
Says who?

504
00:25:33,359 --> 00:25:34,400
We've been submitting properly all along.

505
00:25:34,759 --> 00:25:36,119
Subordinates handle these things.

506
00:25:36,839 --> 00:25:38,240
Who knows if there have been any omissions?

507
00:25:39,519 --> 00:25:40,079
I think,

508
00:25:40,680 --> 00:25:41,599
I should look into it personally.

509
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:49,880
Miss.

510
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:50,559
Nanny Zhao.

511
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:52,319
What did you find?

512
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,240
Mr. Chen is not an outsider.

513
00:25:58,599 --> 00:25:59,559
You may speak freely.

514
00:26:01,119 --> 00:26:01,720
Yes.

515
00:26:02,279 --> 00:26:03,640
Following your instructions, Miss,

516
00:26:03,839 --> 00:26:04,519
I went through everything

517
00:26:04,519 --> 00:26:06,039
your mother brought into the Gu family

518
00:26:06,119 --> 00:26:07,039
item by item.

519
00:26:07,119 --> 00:26:08,359
In one of the boxes,

520
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:09,519
I found this,

521
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:17,359
a receipt for a loan,

522
00:26:20,079 --> 00:26:21,599
Twenty thousand taels of silver.

523
00:26:22,759 --> 00:26:23,839
And who is this

524
00:26:24,039 --> 00:26:24,960
Mrs. Gu?

525
00:26:25,319 --> 00:26:26,440
The old lady of the Gu family.

526
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,119
It was only when I saw this

527
00:26:28,119 --> 00:26:29,000
that I remembered,

528
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:31,559
when your mother married the master,

529
00:26:31,759 --> 00:26:33,160
she had moved into the Daxin Ancestral Clan.

530
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:35,559
One day, Mrs. Gu came,

531
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:37,920
asked the mistress to lend her some money.

532
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,160
The mistress was thin-skinned,

533
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:40,920
and agreed.

534
00:26:41,519 --> 00:26:42,400
Who knows that,

535
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,799
after twenty years,

536
00:26:44,359 --> 00:26:45,720
it still hasn't been repaid?

537
00:26:46,519 --> 00:26:47,799
If Mother isn't in a hurry,

538
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:50,279
no one else will be in a hurry to repay.

539
00:26:52,200 --> 00:26:53,839
Did Mrs. Gu ever mention

540
00:26:54,799 --> 00:26:57,039
what she needed such a large sum for?

541
00:26:57,519 --> 00:26:58,759
I truly don't know.

542
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:00,559
Among noble families in the capital,

543
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:01,880
there's hardly any that doesn't need money.

544
00:27:02,599 --> 00:27:03,839
Families like yours,

545
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,119
well-managed and profitable,

546
00:27:05,279 --> 00:27:06,480
those are few and far between.

547
00:27:06,759 --> 00:27:08,279
Oh, I forgot to tell you,

548
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:10,200
yesterday your father

549
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:11,519
and your sister

550
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,240
moved back to Daxin.

551
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,079
So this means

552
00:27:16,279 --> 00:27:17,440
they're merging into the main house?

553
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:18,920
I suppose so.

554
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,079
Your father,

555
00:27:20,079 --> 00:27:21,640
a widower raising a daughter,

556
00:27:22,359 --> 00:27:24,000
moving back to the main house is proper.

557
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:25,839
As for your main family,

558
00:27:27,359 --> 00:27:28,640
isn't your cousin

559
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:30,640
being matched with the son

560
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:31,279
of Yao Ping, Vice Minister of Justice?

561
00:27:31,519 --> 00:27:32,400
Right now in the capital,

562
00:27:32,599 --> 00:27:33,599
extravagant weddings are in vogue,

563
00:27:34,039 --> 00:27:34,799
and marrying above her station

564
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:35,720
is especially difficult.

565
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:37,279
They must be strapped for cash

566
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:38,559
when it comes to the dowry.

567
00:27:40,599 --> 00:27:41,480
So they've set their sights

568
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:42,680
on our family's money.

569
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:45,400
What a cunning scheme they've got.

570
00:27:47,119 --> 00:27:47,920
But,

571
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,359
they're dealing with me now.

572
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,200
They want to move back to the main house?

573
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:52,599
Then let's all move back together.

574
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,960
Now, this isn't me abusing power.

575
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:12,400
I heard Mr. Chen had come,

576
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:14,480
so I rushed back immediately,

577
00:28:14,839 --> 00:28:16,519
but I still wasn't in time to see him.

578
00:28:18,519 --> 00:28:19,559
He came on business,

579
00:28:19,799 --> 00:28:20,799
and went back today.

580
00:28:21,119 --> 00:28:23,079
He said he had to be on duty tonight.

581
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:26,240
Attendants!

582
00:28:28,599 --> 00:28:30,200
Take this plate of shumai

583
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,279
to the clan school,

584
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,640
for Jinrong.

585
00:28:32,799 --> 00:28:34,079
He studies hard,

586
00:28:34,279 --> 00:28:35,400
and gets hungry easily at night.

587
00:28:35,519 --> 00:28:36,079
Yes.

588
00:28:40,079 --> 00:28:41,279
Mrs. Song is here.

589
00:28:44,079 --> 00:28:45,160
Mother.

590
00:28:48,359 --> 00:28:49,599
Is Mrs. Xu gone?

591
00:28:49,839 --> 00:28:51,160
Yes.

592
00:28:53,319 --> 00:28:54,240
Eat more.

593
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:57,039
You work on business day after day,

594
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:58,440
and have grown much thinner.

595
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,720
I'm not thinner.

596
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:00,799
I'm just stretching out.

597
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:02,079
Is that so?

598
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:03,920
You're growing taller?

599
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:07,480
Later I'll tell the kitchen

600
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:08,559
to make some soup for you,

601
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:09,880
to build you up.

602
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,720
Look how happy you are.

603
00:29:19,319 --> 00:29:20,920
What's the good news?

604
00:29:22,319 --> 00:29:23,960
So you noticed, Mother.

605
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:25,559
Do you know

606
00:29:25,759 --> 00:29:27,160
Mrs. Xu came to see me today

607
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,319
for what?

608
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,160
For what?

609
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:32,839
She came to propose a match for Ji Yao.

610
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,240
Really?

611
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:36,839
From which family?

612
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:39,680
The eldest daughter of the Li family.

613
00:29:39,799 --> 00:29:41,200
That family.

614
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:43,200
She's just average.

615
00:29:45,519 --> 00:29:47,119
I think so.

616
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:49,400
But Mrs. Xu said that

617
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,359
although the business of the Li family

618
00:29:51,359 --> 00:29:53,079
isn't as big as ours,

619
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:55,359
their family is large in number

620
00:29:55,839 --> 00:29:57,319
and harmonious.

621
00:29:58,359 --> 00:30:00,039
The birth mother of the eldest Miss Li,

622
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:01,160
the third Madam,

623
00:30:01,680 --> 00:30:03,400
is a woman of complete good fortune.

624
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:05,720
Besides Miss Li,

625
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:07,519
at her 37 years old,

626
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:09,359
she gave birth to twins.

627
00:30:11,440 --> 00:30:13,440
Now she's nearly 40,

628
00:30:14,119 --> 00:30:17,039
both her parents are still alive.

629
00:30:17,759 --> 00:30:18,559
So,

630
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:21,000
isn't she extremely fortunate?

631
00:30:21,240 --> 00:30:22,400
I was thinking,

632
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:25,359
Ji Yao doesn't have any siblings...

633
00:30:26,839 --> 00:30:28,720
Are you trying to hint at me?

634
00:30:28,799 --> 00:30:30,559
You've misunderstood me, Mother.

635
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:32,680
That wasn't my intention at all.

636
00:30:32,839 --> 00:30:33,680
I...

637
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:36,119
only has one son.

638
00:30:36,519 --> 00:30:37,519
I hope

639
00:30:37,559 --> 00:30:38,640
he can marry

640
00:30:39,079 --> 00:30:40,920
a girl with good fortune.

641
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,519
Auntie,

642
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,839
what exactly do you mean by that?

643
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:48,440
I know,

644
00:30:49,240 --> 00:30:50,400
You're worried that

645
00:30:50,759 --> 00:30:51,440
grandmother

646
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,759
will betroth me to Second Brother?

647
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:56,519
Originally, I didn't want to marry either.

648
00:30:57,319 --> 00:30:58,039
But if you keep

649
00:30:58,039 --> 00:30:59,400
using my deceased mother

650
00:30:59,599 --> 00:31:00,400
to jab at me like this,

651
00:31:01,279 --> 00:31:02,519
I might change my mind.

652
00:31:02,559 --> 00:31:03,039
You...

653
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:04,319
My fate has been unlucky anyway.

654
00:31:04,440 --> 00:31:06,119
So it would be perfect to borrow

655
00:31:06,519 --> 00:31:07,599
some good fortune of Second Brother.

656
00:31:07,759 --> 00:31:08,240
You...

657
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:10,920
Mother.

658
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:11,599
Get out.

659
00:31:12,759 --> 00:31:13,519
Get out!

660
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:26,640
Grandmother,

661
00:31:27,759 --> 00:31:28,799
in a couple of days,

662
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,839
I plan to return to the capital after all.

663
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:35,200
You want to go back to the Gu family?

664
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:38,519
Don't pay any mind

665
00:31:38,599 --> 00:31:40,440
to what your aunt said.

666
00:31:41,119 --> 00:31:42,119
In this household,

667
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:44,200
she doesn't get to call the shots.

668
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:46,039
Not back to Sili Hutong.

669
00:31:46,559 --> 00:31:47,440
Back to

670
00:31:47,759 --> 00:31:48,799
the Daxin ancestral home.

671
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,519
What's going on?

672
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,440
I heard that my father

673
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:56,519
is planning to move back to the main house.

674
00:31:57,839 --> 00:31:58,720
Although

675
00:31:58,759 --> 00:32:00,240
I haven't figured out

676
00:32:00,559 --> 00:32:01,799
the reason yet,

677
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:03,640
I doubt

678
00:32:03,799 --> 00:32:05,319
it's a case of loving mother and dutiful son.

679
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:06,839
You clever girl,

680
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:08,680
with such sharp tongue.

681
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,279
Listen to me.

682
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,160
Nanny Zhao

683
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:12,240
found a receipt for a loan

684
00:32:12,519 --> 00:32:13,759
among my mother's belongings.

685
00:32:14,039 --> 00:32:14,880
A receipt for a loan?

686
00:32:15,839 --> 00:32:17,039
From twenty years ago.

687
00:32:17,279 --> 00:32:18,599
A full twenty thousand taels.

688
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,000
And it turns out my grandmother

689
00:32:20,119 --> 00:32:21,640
borrowed it from my mother personally.

690
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,160
Look at this.

691
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:31,960
When your mother was alive,

692
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:33,119
she never once mentioned this

693
00:32:33,119 --> 00:32:34,640
to me.

694
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:39,400
So you want to go back

695
00:32:40,079 --> 00:32:41,920
to get this money back?

696
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:43,440
Of course I want it back.

697
00:32:43,759 --> 00:32:44,880
Twenty thousand taels,

698
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,519
twenty years of compound interest,

699
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:47,880
how much would that be?

700
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,039
It should be taken back.

701
00:32:54,559 --> 00:32:55,960
It's not just the debt.

702
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:58,799
When your mother married into their family,

703
00:32:58,799 --> 00:32:59,920
the household hadn't been divided yet,

704
00:33:00,119 --> 00:33:02,519
so her dowry were all in Daxin.

705
00:33:03,599 --> 00:33:05,680
Later the family split, they checked assets,

706
00:33:06,079 --> 00:33:07,680
a lot of things were missing.

707
00:33:09,039 --> 00:33:10,039
There was a set of

708
00:33:10,359 --> 00:33:12,000
furniture made of Scented Rosewood

709
00:33:12,799 --> 00:33:14,400
that they actually swapped out

710
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:15,759
for boxwood pieces.

711
00:33:17,400 --> 00:33:18,559
Your mother was too meek.

712
00:33:19,039 --> 00:33:21,279
She just accepted it reluctantly.

713
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:24,799
This time you go to Daxin,

714
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,359
you might as well

715
00:33:26,519 --> 00:33:27,759
demand all of it back.

716
00:33:31,119 --> 00:33:32,440
So,

717
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:34,359
you agree to let me go?

718
00:33:37,839 --> 00:33:39,839
You have a mind of your own.

719
00:33:40,759 --> 00:33:42,000
You know what you should do

720
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:43,319
and what you shouldn't.

721
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:46,279
You've always been sensible.

722
00:33:47,880 --> 00:33:50,319
As much as I hate to see you go,

723
00:33:51,079 --> 00:33:52,359
I also know that

724
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:54,720
a child who is always sheltered at home

725
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:56,119
will never amount to much.

726
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:57,720
If you must go,

727
00:33:58,240 --> 00:33:59,400
then go.

728
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:03,039
But remember that

729
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,880
grandmother's home

730
00:34:05,079 --> 00:34:06,359
is your home too.

731
00:34:06,559 --> 00:34:07,519
Whenever

732
00:34:07,519 --> 00:34:09,200
you want to come back, just come back.

733
00:34:09,720 --> 00:34:10,559
Remember?

734
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,719
Yes.

735
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,159
Grandmother,

736
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:19,199
the person I'll miss most is you.

737
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:23,599
I'll miss you too, my child.

738
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:27,400
Thank you.

739
00:34:33,679 --> 00:34:34,119
Lord,

740
00:34:34,559 --> 00:34:35,559
the old gatekeeper said that

741
00:34:35,639 --> 00:34:36,880
Mr. Gu's family moved back to the main house.

742
00:34:37,119 --> 00:34:37,719
A few days ago,

743
00:34:37,719 --> 00:34:38,880
the whole family moved to Daxin.

744
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,639
What about Gu Jinzhao?

745
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:44,280
She arrived in the capital yesterday,

746
00:34:44,599 --> 00:34:45,599
came here first,

747
00:34:45,599 --> 00:34:46,480
packed some things,

748
00:34:46,599 --> 00:34:47,800
and left for Daxin this morning.

749
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:51,159
That ungrateful woman.

750
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:52,079
She moves

751
00:34:52,079 --> 00:34:52,880
and doesn't even bother to tell me?

752
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:58,519
Grandmother.

753
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:03,079
Take a seat.

754
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:05,960
Thank you, grandmother.

755
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:09,920
Why didn't you bring Ji Rong

756
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:10,920
back with you?

757
00:35:12,079 --> 00:35:14,639
The Ji family is the maternal relatives,

758
00:35:15,039 --> 00:35:16,199
and they're merchants.

759
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:17,559
Ji Rong

760
00:35:17,639 --> 00:35:19,280
is the only son of Dezhao.

761
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:20,840
He'll have to sit for the imperial exams.

762
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:23,199
He can't spend all his time

763
00:35:23,199 --> 00:35:24,920
together with a bunch of businessmen.

764
00:35:25,199 --> 00:35:26,239
He needs to come back

765
00:35:26,519 --> 00:35:28,320
and focus on studies, that's the right path.

766
00:35:28,639 --> 00:35:31,159
I agree with that.

767
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:34,519
Grandmother,

768
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:36,719
although the Ji family are merchants,

769
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:38,360
their clan school

770
00:35:38,519 --> 00:35:40,239
is renowned even here in the capital.

771
00:35:41,079 --> 00:35:42,199
Even Chen Xuanqing

772
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:44,280
once studied there.

773
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:46,400
Why can't Ji Rong?

774
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:48,599
Besides,

775
00:35:48,719 --> 00:35:49,400
it's not like Ji Rong

776
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,400
didn't come back to the capital.

777
00:35:50,719 --> 00:35:51,679
He just went straight

778
00:35:51,679 --> 00:35:53,119
to the Qifang Hutong academy.

779
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:56,360
So Ji Rong did come back?

780
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:57,960
Why didn't he

781
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:58,960
come here first?

782
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:00,320
Whose idea was this?

783
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:01,920
Grandmother,

784
00:36:02,239 --> 00:36:03,440
it was mine.

785
00:36:03,679 --> 00:36:04,639
Your idea?

786
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,639
Without a mistress in the household,

787
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:11,679
surely you lack proper upbringing.

788
00:36:12,679 --> 00:36:13,280
Dezhao,

789
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,440
Gu Lan and Gu Jinzhao

790
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:16,199
have both grown up now.

791
00:36:16,519 --> 00:36:17,079
I'll send

792
00:36:17,079 --> 00:36:18,400
the matrons from my household

793
00:36:19,159 --> 00:36:20,440
to teach them

794
00:36:20,599 --> 00:36:21,760
proper manners and etiquette,

795
00:36:23,239 --> 00:36:24,800
so they don't embarrass themselves

796
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:26,000
when it's time to arrange marriages.

797
00:36:26,679 --> 00:36:27,360
Grandmother,

798
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,280
we have just finished our mourning period.

799
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:31,239
Why the sudden rush to arrange marriages?

800
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,440
Is this

801
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:35,000
the main house's manners and etiquette?

802
00:36:36,079 --> 00:36:37,039
Then perhaps we'd better not be taught.

803
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:38,760
Jinzhao.

804
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:44,320
Mother,

805
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:47,320
Jinzhao has only just returned home.

806
00:36:47,719 --> 00:36:49,119
If she's done something wrong,

807
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:51,679
we can correct her gradually.

808
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:54,679
Jinzhao,

809
00:36:55,159 --> 00:36:56,639
I heard from your father

810
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:58,480
that you're now managing

811
00:36:58,480 --> 00:37:00,119
the accounts of your family.

812
00:37:01,239 --> 00:37:01,960
Nanny Zhao.

813
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:12,039
All the household accounts are here.

814
00:37:12,519 --> 00:37:13,960
It's just that my mother

815
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:14,880
was bedridden for years

816
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:15,960
and neglected them,

817
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:17,760
and my father

818
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:19,239
has been focused on his official career,

819
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:21,000
so the income hasn't been much.

820
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:23,079
Hope aunt won't hold it against us.

821
00:37:23,599 --> 00:37:25,239
Of course not.

822
00:37:30,639 --> 00:37:31,880
Madam,

823
00:37:32,079 --> 00:37:33,159
Lord Ye is here.

824
00:37:33,639 --> 00:37:34,760
What does he want?

825
00:37:36,639 --> 00:37:37,679
Did he say why he came?

826
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:38,599
No.

827
00:37:39,639 --> 00:37:40,440
You may go.

828
00:37:40,599 --> 00:37:41,119
Yes.

829
00:37:44,559 --> 00:37:45,960
Why is he here?

830
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,079
Could it be that our family

831
00:37:48,079 --> 00:37:49,639
has run into some trouble, mother?

832
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,000
Nonsense.

833
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:52,719
If there were any trouble,

834
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:54,920
your aunt would have sent word.

835
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,079
What's wrong?

836
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:59,679
Doesn't the Young Lord come here often?

837
00:38:00,719 --> 00:38:01,559
Jinzhao,

838
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:02,920
you might not know,

839
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,840
Lord Ye

840
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:06,760
has joined the Criminal Investigation Bureau.

841
00:38:07,159 --> 00:38:08,280
All he does every day

842
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:10,199
is seizing properties and executing people.

843
00:38:10,519 --> 00:38:11,760
We're all scared of him.

844
00:38:12,519 --> 00:38:13,719
Even your Uncle Deyuan

845
00:38:13,719 --> 00:38:15,000
gets nervous when he sees him.

846
00:38:15,159 --> 00:38:15,840
Your grandmother already

847
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:17,159
asked your aunt

848
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:19,039
to tell him not to come for a while.

849
00:38:20,559 --> 00:38:21,320
Mother,

850
00:38:21,679 --> 00:38:23,199
he is still the Young Lord.

851
00:38:23,719 --> 00:38:24,519
Perhaps...

852
00:38:25,039 --> 00:38:26,719
perhaps we should go out to greet him.

853
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:29,679
Greet him what?

854
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:31,920
He's a junior.

855
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:34,039
Why would I bow to him?

856
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:35,880
Nanny Su.

857
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:36,559
Yes.

858
00:38:37,119 --> 00:38:37,719
You just

859
00:38:38,119 --> 00:38:39,440
tell him to go to his sister's room.

860
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:40,639
No need to come here.

861
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:41,760
No need to what?

862
00:38:47,199 --> 00:38:49,239
Greetings, Young Lord.

863
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:51,440
Madam, please.

864
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:53,239
I am merely a junior.

865
00:38:53,719 --> 00:38:54,840
I wouldn't dare accept such a bow.

866
00:38:56,519 --> 00:38:58,239
You jest, Young Lord.

867
00:38:58,519 --> 00:38:59,360
Bowing to you

868
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,159
is only proper.

869
00:39:14,159 --> 00:39:15,159
I'm here for you.

870
00:39:15,599 --> 00:39:16,239
Come out.

871
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:17,679
I have something to tell you.

872
00:39:37,239 --> 00:39:37,840
Ye Xian.

873
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:47,920
What,

874
00:39:48,519 --> 00:39:49,760
do you find me frightening too?

875
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:51,760
Since when did your ears

876
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:52,840
get so sharp?

877
00:39:53,239 --> 00:39:54,320
We were talking far away from you,

878
00:39:54,519 --> 00:39:55,519
and you could still hear it.

879
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,519
Our bureau gathers intelligence

880
00:39:58,639 --> 00:39:59,639
and monitors all officials.

881
00:40:00,079 --> 00:40:01,719
Listening in on people's conversations

882
00:40:02,079 --> 00:40:02,920
is exactly the job.

883
00:40:04,760 --> 00:40:05,719
Really?

884
00:40:07,639 --> 00:40:08,320
Of course not.

885
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:09,360
I held a knife

886
00:40:09,360 --> 00:40:10,599
to that servant girl's throat.

887
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,360
Of course she didn't dare make a sound,

888
00:40:13,199 --> 00:40:14,199
and let me stand outside the door

889
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:15,360
and listen

890
00:40:15,639 --> 00:40:16,360
all I wanted.

891
00:40:17,679 --> 00:40:18,800
Why must you do this?

892
00:40:22,039 --> 00:40:23,360
Can you say something original?

893
00:40:23,719 --> 00:40:24,400
Why must you do this?

894
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,320
Why do you have to do that?

895
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:26,320
What's the reason for this?

896
00:40:27,119 --> 00:40:28,880
Ever since I joined this Bureau

897
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:31,119
I've grown tired of hearing all of these.

898
00:40:33,559 --> 00:40:34,360
Fine, fine, fine.

899
00:40:34,559 --> 00:40:35,639
I won't say it anymore.

900
00:40:38,519 --> 00:40:39,239
What's this?

901
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:43,800
I just captured two imperial criminals.

902
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:45,000
Drew a bit of blood.

903
00:40:47,119 --> 00:40:47,679
What,

904
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:49,840
too gruesome for you?

905
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:51,480
Enough.

906
00:40:51,880 --> 00:40:52,559
Go to the guest courtyard

907
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:54,039
and change out of that robe.

908
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,320
Ye Xian, stop right there.

909
00:40:59,039 --> 00:41:00,760
Do you believe I'll never speak to you again?

910
00:41:13,519 --> 00:41:14,199
Alright.

911
00:41:15,400 --> 00:41:16,000
I know you...

912
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:16,719
No, you don't.

913
00:41:20,199 --> 00:41:21,559
Why did you have to take this path?

914
00:41:25,599 --> 00:41:26,920
Because I need power.

915
00:41:28,079 --> 00:41:28,920
I need followers.

916
00:41:31,440 --> 00:41:32,119
Then couldn't you...

917
00:41:32,119 --> 00:41:32,599
No.

918
00:41:33,559 --> 00:41:34,320
I've thought it over.

919
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:36,079
There's no other way.

920
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:38,639
This is the only path I can take

921
00:41:38,639 --> 00:41:39,840
to preserve the Marquis's.

922
00:41:51,159 --> 00:41:52,039
This is...

923
00:41:52,679 --> 00:41:53,599
A bracelet.

924
00:41:55,159 --> 00:41:56,159
Confiscated from a raided house.

925
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:57,760
It's already been registered,

926
00:41:58,320 --> 00:41:59,280
so you can wear it without worry.

927
00:42:02,719 --> 00:42:04,360
If you find it too tainted,

928
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:05,599
you can throw it away.

929
00:43:12,840 --> 00:43:13,559
Sorry, Gu Lian.

930
00:43:13,559 --> 00:43:14,639
That really hurt.

931
00:43:16,199 --> 00:43:17,960
S-sorry.

932
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:22,079
If you let me poke you back,

933
00:43:22,239 --> 00:43:23,039
then I'll forgive you.

934
00:43:24,559 --> 00:43:25,480
Gu Lian,

935
00:43:25,960 --> 00:43:27,159
I didn't mean to.

936
00:43:28,039 --> 00:43:28,760
Didn't mean to?

937
00:43:28,760 --> 00:43:29,800
But you still poked me.

938
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:30,920
What?

939
00:43:31,639 --> 00:43:32,920
If you're not willing,

940
00:43:33,159 --> 00:43:34,559
I'll go tell grandmother

941
00:43:34,840 --> 00:43:36,280
and let her judge.

942
00:43:36,599 --> 00:43:37,960
Weren't you still planning

943
00:43:38,039 --> 00:43:39,119
to have me help you ask grandmother

944
00:43:39,119 --> 00:43:40,360
for a good marriage match?

945
00:43:40,559 --> 00:43:41,920
Forget it.

946
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:50,480
Wait.

947
00:43:53,440 --> 00:43:54,559
What gives you the right to poke her?

948
00:43:56,119 --> 00:43:57,679
You tripped her on purpose.

949
00:43:58,079 --> 00:43:59,400
Her bumping into you was an accident,

950
00:43:59,760 --> 00:44:00,880
so you deserved it.

951
00:44:02,199 --> 00:44:03,239
So what?

952
00:44:03,400 --> 00:44:04,559
I'm the one who got hurt.

953
00:44:04,559 --> 00:44:05,960
I have every right to poke her back.

954
00:44:06,199 --> 00:44:06,760
What,

955
00:44:07,280 --> 00:44:08,199
you're going to help her?

956
00:44:08,840 --> 00:44:09,320
Fine.

957
00:44:09,840 --> 00:44:11,000
Then poking you is fine too.

958
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:12,079
How dare you?

959
00:44:13,719 --> 00:44:14,920
Grandmother is always going on about

960
00:44:14,920 --> 00:44:16,000
manners and rules.

961
00:44:16,599 --> 00:44:17,599
I thought the main house's rules

962
00:44:17,599 --> 00:44:18,639
must be exceptional.

963
00:44:19,760 --> 00:44:20,480
But it seems

964
00:44:20,760 --> 00:44:22,000
there's nothing special.

965
00:44:23,880 --> 00:44:25,519
Don't try to provoke me with your words.

966
00:44:25,760 --> 00:44:27,039
That doesn't work on me.

967
00:44:27,800 --> 00:44:28,400
Really?

968
00:44:30,599 --> 00:44:31,639
I heard you just had your

969
00:44:31,639 --> 00:44:32,719
preliminary betrothal with the Yao family.

970
00:44:33,039 --> 00:44:34,440
The Yao house is a family of Vice Minister,

971
00:44:34,440 --> 00:44:35,519
a household of poetry and propriety.

972
00:44:35,920 --> 00:44:37,519
If they learned their future daughter-in-law

973
00:44:37,599 --> 00:44:38,880
is this violent and unreasonable,

974
00:44:39,119 --> 00:44:40,280
with no care for family bonds,

975
00:44:41,039 --> 00:44:42,559
I wonder if they'd come to regret

976
00:44:42,559 --> 00:44:43,920
this marriage arrangement.

977
00:44:45,840 --> 00:44:47,440
Have you completely lost your mind?

978
00:44:47,719 --> 00:44:48,519
Stop!

979
00:44:50,960 --> 00:44:51,639
Gu Lian.

980
00:44:51,840 --> 00:44:52,440
Grandmother.

981
00:44:52,440 --> 00:44:53,599
Jinzhao makes a valid point.

982
00:44:55,599 --> 00:44:56,840
Grandmother.

983
00:44:56,840 --> 00:44:58,559
Since Jinzhao is so reasonable,

984
00:44:59,280 --> 00:45:00,239
why don't just come serve

985
00:45:00,239 --> 00:45:01,400
your old grandmother,

986
00:45:01,599 --> 00:45:02,840
and massage my legs?

987
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:13,760
Grandmother,

988
00:45:14,880 --> 00:45:16,000
is this pressure alright?

989
00:45:21,599 --> 00:45:22,440
Comfortable.

990
00:45:25,079 --> 00:45:26,559
Since you're relaxed,

991
00:45:27,159 --> 00:45:29,000
may I discuss something with you?

992
00:45:30,840 --> 00:45:31,599
What is it?

993
00:45:33,679 --> 00:45:34,920
Twenty years ago,

994
00:45:35,239 --> 00:45:36,280
my mother lent you

995
00:45:36,280 --> 00:45:37,519
twenty thousand taels of silver.

996
00:45:39,079 --> 00:45:40,719
When do you plan to repay it?

997
00:45:43,239 --> 00:45:44,719
What twenty thousand taels?

998
00:45:45,840 --> 00:45:47,039
What nonsense are you talking?
